#: cambalache/app/cmb_help_window.ui:981
msgid "Prefixes"
msgstr ""

#: cambalache/app/cmb_help_window.ui:992
msgid ""
"A GResources file can have one or multiple prefixes containing multiple "
"files and are added from the resource property editor."
