#: cambalache/app/cmb_help_window.ui:1002
#, fuzzy
msgid "Adding files"
msgstr "Ajouter un nouveau fichier d'interface"

#: cambalache/app/cmb_help_window.ui:1013
msgid ""
"Files can be added from a prefix property editor. Once a new file is added "
"the filename and its properties can be set in the editor.\n"
"\n"
"More information about how GResources works is available <a href=\"https://"
"docs.gtk.org/gio/struct.Resource.html\" title=\"https://docs.gtk.org/gio/"
